      "created": "2019-01-24T00:02:10.434+0000",
      "description": "A number of people have developed go client library for HDFS.  [Example 1|https://medium.com/sqooba/making-hdfs-a-hundred-times-faster-ac75b8b5e0b4] [Example 2|https://github.com/colinmarc/hdfs].\r\n\r\nThis can be enhanced into a real storage driver for Docker registry.",
