      "comment": {
        "comments": [
          {
            "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/13211409/comment/16755444",
            "id": "16755444",
            "author": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=eyang",
              "name": "eyang",
              "key": "eyang",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Eric Yang",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Thanks to [~shanekumpf@gmail.com], I was able to rebase his [hdfs docker driver|https://github.com/sakserv/distribution] for Docker Registry to latest Docker registry code, and run the same benchmark as YARN-9229.  The performance is quite good:\r\n\r\n| | Remote | Local |\r\n| Pull | 18.673s | 13.109s |\r\n| Push | 26.113s | 25.917s |\r\n\r\nThe numbers are measured on the same hardware that was used to measure NFS Gateway flavor of Docker Registry.\r\n\r\nThe only drawback of this approach is Go HDFS client library does not fully support Kerberos enabled environment.  User will encounter [\"unexpected sequence number\"|https://github.com/colinmarc/hdfs/issues/144] issue.  Some GSSAPI encryption related problems that are not fully resolved in Colin's Go HDFS library.\r\n",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=eyang",
              "name": "eyang",
              "key": "eyang",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Eric Yang",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "created": "2019-01-29T22:44:11.877+0000",
            "updated": "2019-01-29T22:44:11.877+0000"
          },
          {
